Day in the Life of Thor:

Sit in chair.

Beam to other places in chair.

Fly around the galaxy enforcing the treaty with the Goa'uld in the spiffy new ship.

Beam O'Neill aboard for a little chit chat.

Eat yellow styrofoam-like cubes for dinner.

Ponder the replicator situation.

Blink.

Start over.
